{
  "stem": "13219.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he took me so he can send me back with the men who he was working for, to bring some bread and vegetables home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which, when I went with him they never searched the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this particular day I set out in the morning to bring some bread and something to my mother, and I saw a lot of people marching from the-- from the field, before we come into the city.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Marching-- Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the city, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the man who-- who I was riding with told me, he said, every time you see somebody just turn the head-- turn yourself away from him, and I'll see if I can do something, because they are killing the Jews in the city.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were Jews, marched by very few Germans, most of them Ukrainian police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were marching to-- and there were three graves dug, which I find out later, and they were-- they were shooting them and putting them into the grave.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went in the grave, they shoot them, and then other people went in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how they killed them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, about 3,400 people, or 3,500 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They killed them in one day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Men, women, children, everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the city.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They marched them, and they told them to take their belongings, whatever, because they're going to work in a camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And instead of that, they marched them down to the field, and they told them to undress, and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was positive that they wouldn't kill them, because my dad made a couple of hiding places, and he divided family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took my mother and my sister and put them in one hiding place, and--",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
